            "a3": "<p>IPX6 rated \u2014 it handles heavy rain, splashes, and brief submersion. You can use it in storms, on boats, or dropped in a puddle. It's not meant for diving or long underwater use.</p>",
            "q4": "How long does the battery last?",
            "a4": "<p>6-10 hours of continuous runtime depending on mode. High beam drains faster, Low beam and Tail Light last longer. The LCD display shows exact battery percentage so you always know when to recharge \u2014 no more dying flashlight at 3am.</p>",
