            "a6": "<p>Front is a focused spotlight (up to 1,000m range) with adjustable zoom \u2014 for searching, signaling, or lighting far distances. Rear COB is a wide flood light \u2014 for close-range hands-free work like reading a map, changing a tire, or lighting a workspace. Both run independently.</p>",
            "q7": "Is this a good gift?",
            "a7": "<p>It's one of our top gift items. Comes in a premium gift box with everything included. Perfect for dads, outdoor enthusiasts, preppers, or anyone who values being prepared. Opens to a proper presentation \u2014 not a plastic bag.</p>",
